{
  "texts": [
    "Open access to GenAIs like ChatGPT would have a high potential for levelling the playing field.",
    "However, ChatGPT and other GenAI alike now offer users the option to paid subscription services, which give better answers [22].",
    "These subscription fees are quite high (e.g.",
    "20 dollars per month for GPT Plus [23]), especially for early career researchers and researchers from low-income countries.",
    "The monetisation of knowledge is an alarming development, as inequal access to high-quality knowledge will inevitably lead to disparities, at the cost of the most vulnerable researchers [6,27].Despite these issues, there is no denying that GenAI tools have incredible potential to advance academic writing."
  ]
}